txt.en: 'I wonder if it has been decided whether Lobelia Sackville-Baggins or Holly Hornblower will plan the feasts this year?'
'I am so glad that Old Flourdumpling is partial to my parties...it might keep Lobelia Sackville-Baggins from interfering!'
'This neighbourhood will have some of the best festivals this year!'
'Oh! I need to order more beer for my next party!'
